# Core Conventions

- Use JavaScript JSX (`.jsx`) � do not convert to TypeScript unless asked
- Import alias: `@/*` maps to `src/*`
- Use named exports for components
- Merge Tailwind classes with `cn()` from `@/lib/utils`
- Put feature logic in `src/features/*`
- Put static mock data in `src/data/*`
- Put shared UI primitives in `src/components/ui/*`
- Put page shell in `src/app/App.jsx`
- Brand name in UI: **JB Fit Blueprint**
